      unexport ip_conntrack_{,un}register_notifier
      snd_mem_proc_read(): convert to list_for_each_entry*
      Linux 2.6.16.55-rc1
Andi Kleen (1):
      x86_64: Zero extend all registers after ptrace in 32bit entry path (CVE-2007-4573)
